title: Kiss Person Man Dark Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Represents a tender kiss between two men, where both have dark to medium-dark skin tones. This emoji signifies love, romance, and partnership within the LGBTQ+ community.

Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and smooth gradients lend a warm, inviting glow to their skin tones and the subtle blush on their cheeks, while soft rounded edges ensure a gentle and romantic depiction. This emoji on Apple devices is a powerful and inclusive way to express deep affection, romantic love, or a passionate kiss between a couple.
